data.chText: 我们星期天一般不在家。

ex.chText: 这个小国家大部分地区位于沙漠中。
ex.enText: This small country is largely located in the desert.
Her success was largely due to luck.

synonyms.bx: 指范围或程度上占大半地。
指作为非常重要的成分但并非全部地。

ex.chText: 他的善良令我极为感动。
ex.enText: I was greatly moved by his kindness.

synonyms.bx: 主要用于强化程度，不修饰形容词，通常用于动词或分词前。

ex.chText: 该党的成员大部分为工人。
ex.enText: The members of the party are mostly workers.

ex.chText: 参加聚会的男子大都非常年轻。
ex.enText: The men at the party were mostly fairly young.

ex.chText: 我们星期六一般不在家。
ex.enText: We mostly go out on Saturdays.

example: by and large it doesn't rain much here

value.def: You use mostly to indicate that a statement is generally true, for example true about the majority of a group of things or people, true most of the time, or true in most respects.

example.ex: I am working with mostly highly motivated people...
example.tran: 和我共事的人大多积极性极高。
轿车的大部分部件是金属制造的。
大多为30多岁的男男女女

example.ex: Her own twelve pictures sold fairly well, mostly to friends and family...
example.tran: 她自己的12幅画卖得相当好，多半卖给了朋友和家人。

example.ex: They have mostly invested their money in expensive real estate.
example.tran: 他们已把钱主要投资到昂贵的房地产业了。

trans: 美味关系；甜蜜蜜；爱情美味甜蜜蜜；美味情缘；厨房的秘密
交响音乐会；特音乐节；莫扎特再现
